# ── Runtime workflow data ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Generated by Seed, Forge, Archy, Chisel. Overwritten each session.
# These are artifacts, not source.
.squad/forge/
.squad/prd/
.squad/scout-cache.md
.squad/chisel-config.json
.squad/lore-config.json

# .squad/architecture.md and .squad/decisions.md are authored by you —
# commit them if you want to version-control your project context.

# ── Second-brain vault ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Personal, cross-project, tool-agnostic. Lives outside any repo by design.
# Guard against accidentally nesting it here.
second-brain/

# ── Claude Code local config ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Machine-local settings (API keys, personal overrides). Never commit.
.claude/settings.local.json

# Working copies of agents/skills installed directly under .claude/ at the
# project root. These shadow the canonical claude/ tree during development
# and are not part of the distributable.
.claude/agents/
.claude/skills/

# ── macOS ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
